comments: Noel (OKC) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
James (LAL) makes marginal contact with Noel (OKC) that does not prevent him from defending the shot.
Green (LAL) steps on the baseline while in possession of the ball.
Noel (OKC) sets the pick in Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
James (LAL) cleanly blocks the ball on Gallinari's (OKC) driving shot attempt.
Schroder (OKC) and Rondo (LAL) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Noel (OKC) sets the screen in Green's (LAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Paul (OKC) collapses his arms and absorbs contact from James (LAL) as he sets the screen.
Gallinari (OKC) lands in a legal jump stop, after which he is allowed to pivot on either foot, and he maintains his pivot foot.
Paul (OKC) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
Davis (LAL) and Noel (OKC) briefly engage and disengage with one another during the rebound.
Davis (LAL) and Gallinari (OKC) engage and separate off-ball.
Gallinari (OKC) is firming up in a picking position in Rondo's (LAL) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the pick.
James (LAL) makes marginal contact with Noel's (OKC) body during his shooting motion on the play at the basket.
